bf08c5dd2665c81c759a83224e1.jpg&h=52244749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfeel到會有超能力大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想起佢係Web版最後果幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過WEB版同書籍版個背景完全係兩個人</blockquote><br />\n除左主角下場之登我冇睇web版<br />\n求細粉字劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我淨係睇書睇到佢就算死左老豆都冇發奮做人咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"57ddf80d7f76cec538977131c9c1375e291d3a3c","tid":181120,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T16:01:30.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>仲以為佢最尾個集會改做成功出動完左場戰爭 完左套動畫佢算<br />\n最尾仲繼續講之後發展 睇黎想繼續出落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n個收尾開放式咋，未必會出架</blockquote><br />\n如果真係出第二季我覺得用翻上一集主角唔比用V1 ，之後鏡頭轉到英國決定參戰，戴lego帶領人馬反擊，大叔個女決意做志願兵好啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n未必會出,但係有機會出<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n出嘅話講打俄佬會好怪<br />\n動畫冇講佢啲經濟理論<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"230f96bbff5b38b62b30520615dc91515b987594","tid":181120,"uid":30347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:40:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/102441_2029abf08c5dd2665c81c759a83224e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F102441_2029abf08c5dd2665c81c759a83224e1.jpg&h=52244749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfeel到會有超能力大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想起佢係Web版最後果幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過WEB版同書籍版個背景完全係兩個人</blockquote><br />\n除左主角下場之登我冇睇web版<br />\n求細粉字劇透<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我淨係睇書睇到佢就算死左老豆都冇發奮做人咁嘅樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-small;\">在web版中佢係合眾國人，在故事後期中特然出現並成為主角感到棘手的人。由於是狂信徒的關係，跟主角誓不兩立。主角利用這個特點，把瑪利蘇多次引到聯軍之中製造Friendly fire ,令聯軍士兵對她有仇。最後在大戰末期，在一次與主角的戰鬥團戰鬥之後被聯軍中對她有仇的士兵們以魔力刀一人一刀把當時傷痕累累的瑪利蘇捅死。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d8441a50a1fcb7664831b9d89391dda1c0af5648","tid":181120,"uid":30745,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-01T17:46:14.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/04/01/102441_2029abf08c5dd2665c81c759a83224e1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F04%2F01%2F102441_2029abf08c5dd2665c81c759a83224e1.jpg&h=52244749&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/yipes.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nfeel到會有超能力大戰<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n想起佢係Web版最後果幕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomo